                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8377" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1292</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2138 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">接二连三“拆”，一“拆”抵万金？——大族激光分拆子公司上市之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Carve-outs one after another, one split is worth a fortune？——the path of Han&#39;s Laser&#39;s subsidiaries carve-outs</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">田冠军，杨倩，王晓晖</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大族激光科技产业集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大族激光；分拆上市；企业价值；分拆动因；市场反应</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Han&#39;s Laser; Carve-outs; Enterprise value；Motivation analysis; Market response</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在2019年出台分拆上市政策新规后，A股市场分拆上市持续升温，甚至存在多次分拆子公司上市的现象，然而实践中分拆上市一定能一“拆”抵万金吗？作为A股较为激进的“分拆专业户”，大族激光三连“拆”旗下优质子公司冲击创业板IPO备受瞩目，而频繁分拆后大族激光的业绩表现并不卖座。首次分拆大族数控上市后，同年大族激光营收净利双降，市值几近腰斩，引发了资本市场有关其“过度分拆”的质疑。本案例以“大族激光分拆上市后是否提升企业价值”为分析主线，对其分拆动因、市场反应、经济后果、存在的问题等方面做出了详细阐述，旨在引导学生理解分拆上市动因的相关理论，掌握常见的企业绩效评价方法和企业价值评估方法，加强对分拆上市这一策略和手段的理性思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After the introduction of new policies and regulations for carve-outs in 2019, the A-share market&#39;s carve-outs has continued to heat up, and there have even been multiple instances of carve-outs of subsidiary companies. However, in practice, can one split always be &quot; worth a fortune&quot;? As a more aggressive &quot;carve-outs specialist&quot; in the A-share market, Han&#39;s Laser &quot;three consecutive carve-outs&quot; of its high-quality subsidiaries hit the GEM IPO in the spotlight. However, after frequent carve-outs, Han&#39;s Laser&#39;s performance has not sold well. After the initial carve-out of Han&#39;s CNC, the net revenue and profit of Han&#39;s Laser decreased in the same year, sparking doubts in the capital market about its &quot;excessive carve-outs&quot;. This case takes &quot;whether the carve-outs of Han&#39;s Laser enhance enterprise value&quot; as the main line of analysis, focusing on its carve-outs motives, market reactions, economic consequences, and problems analysis. The aim is to guide students to understand the relevant theories of the carve-outs and listing reasons, master common methods of enterprise performance evaluation and enterprise value evaluation, and strengthen rational thinking on the strategy and means of carve-outs listing.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《资本运营》、《财务管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资产重组方式；融资约束理论；信息不对称理论；核心化战略理论；企业经济效果评价方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
